Avoid a build error when the platform file does not exist. Report the exception when throwing the error to make diagnostic easier. CheckModel reported errors on String/string type, accept quick fixes.
Remove dependency on sandbox from org.campagnelab.bdval language. The language does not depend on the sandbox, it is the other way around.

Adjust language dependencies. bdval must extend baseLanguage because its generator produces nodes in the baseLanguage language. Remove dependency on jetbrains.mps.lang.project.modules that was not used.
Merged remote changes
Merged remote changes, added prostated example solution
Udpated method to generate sequence files, started generating final model sequence files
Changed way sequence files are generated, also generate final-model sequence files now
Added JFrame to show when running evaluate statistics and generate final model

Sample approaches set by intention on approach section. Changed JFrame shown when running evaluate so that long tag descriptions are readable. More informative error messages. added info/instructions.
Displays results of entire project folder, more checks/error messages to make sure user fills out everything needed
Fixed error so multiple projects in sandbox do not conflict with each other when running
Final Model, fixed so all feature selections will generate final model, documented code
Added infos
Moved status section
Make updateStatus a bit more resilient to unusual directory structures. Correct typo in editor.
